            . I have known him eight or nine years; he was a boy under me, as a waiter at the Rainbow tavern, Temple Bar; he lived there four or five months; he always behaved well there; he had always a good character to the present time.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17730113-19-person233">
