            . I have known him five years; I never heard any harm of him; he is a hard working lad.</p>
               <p>Q. to Humphreys. What business are you?</p>
               <p>Humphreys. A journeyman taylor.</p>
               <p>Q. What can you earn a week at your trade?</p>
               <p>Humphreys. Fifteen shillings and nine pence.</p>
