            . I was robbed in a returned pot chaise last Wednesday was week, in the Hampstead road, near the end of <placeName id="t17730113-19-crimeloc108">Big-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17730113-19-crimeloc108" type="placeName" value="Big-lane"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17730113-19-crimeloc108" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
