                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17730113-19-off106 t17730113-19-crimeloc108"></join>, two footpads stopt the chaise; they came to the door and obliged me to let down the glass; then they demanded my money; I gave them a guinea, a half guinea, and a crown piece; one of them held a pistol to my breast, which frightened me so much that I made no observation on his person.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17730113-19-person241">
                  John
                   Samuel
